Number and variable types:
--------------------------
var x = 2+3;
val x=23
val x: Byte=5 //Explicit
val life:Long=42
val life=4L
val z = 6.9F
val z:Float = 6.9F

println("total price is $totalPrice")

Byte, Short , Int , Long, Float, Double

- By default all decimals are double, All small nos are int and all big nos are Long.

